{ { NORTH MALVERN C.E. PRIMARY SCHOOL }
The information for this account of Suckley and district was gathered by the children of Class 7 of North Malvern C.E. School, under the guidance of the Deputy Head Teacher, Mrs. R.A.Johnson.
They wish to thank all those who gave so freely of their time, includ- ing the parents who provided transport and support, the Managing Director of the Bruff Manufacturing Company, the Postmistress of Longley Green, the 'official' photographer, Mr. R. Wilson and last, but by no means least, the school secretary, Mrs. B. Yardley.
